{"tid":1598654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣】文宣下一步應該打「信心危機」「香港已無執法機構」","createTime":"2019-09-27T14:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T15:12:10.000Z","uid":33930,"like":97,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"92f5f36c8673ba9f15ce09059de288d28c0d4ba2","tid":1598654,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"如果仲係講緊<span style=\"color: red;\">「警黑合作」「執法不公」</span><br />\n姐係仲承認緊警犬「執法機構」既地位<br />\n有鑑於而家警犬既信任程度已經足夠地低<br />\n&quot;鶳&quot;都慢慢入屋<br />\n文宣係時候走前一步，打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「信心危機」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">口號好簡單︰「面對現實，香港已無執法機構」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁樣先可以引導民意進一步剝奪警犬既<span style=\"color: red;\">合法性</span><br />\n陳浩天被襲後，表明不會報案<br />\n唔理佢係咪淨係識聲明好，起麻佢以身作則<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳哩個諗法出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfffdfd0600313bc117cd631723fc7e593315969","tid":1598654,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f615d5d8e5138127dd4360c6a3b09dd34787c63d","tid":1598654,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ce24eab758ab7c30a590254f55b286f7ee7b930","tid":1598654,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:48:45.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"72f592192a48405601997296648c45b04078b583","tid":1598654,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:48:54.000Z","msg":"低成本高效抗爭！&mdash;&mdash;檢舉有害facebook page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1598629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1598629</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"55aba0354f435391504639468ad78ee288d0526e","tid":1598654,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"089280edc7ebc56551fffbad49b791f232b07481","tid":